{"tid":1149353,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔子幫自己洗腳 :D","createTime":"2019-05-11T06:01:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T14:10:29.000Z","uid":197098,"like":9,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5c02eae5623895edb2a93c3a93c2466f255118a9","tid":1149353,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:01:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/45p3Exbf4So\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F45p3Exbf4So&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=b5e3f47f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/45p3Exbf4So</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kqofztfWKno\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkqofztfWKno&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=44c15767\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kqofztfWKno</a>"},{"pid":"f6ff77d69cb7b0d00f42d732e33982564e6e9e7f","tid":1149353,"uid":199120,"like":5,"dislike":23,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"子你老母，小學雞定大陸哩呀？"},{"pid":"447140d27823e9546771c71cc26616cb921744ce","tid":1149353,"uid":189798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:20:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e92dea4d42f0473d0eab5b16e7a70cccf0bc1fd5","tid":1149353,"uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T07:46:21.000Z","msg":"兔子是其中一種最心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們尤其是咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是兔子的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響的。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n以下video可看到兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人！☺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=a667f47e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a>"},{"pid":"5e9bc9afe0f6871f6331e868b2891b487f6b9ff7","tid":1149353,"uid":33878,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T08:00:35.000Z","msg":"我個隻都會<br />\n病從口入呀<br />\n屌極都唔聽"},{"pid":"9062c84d09cbbbec14bf889b1359d2fc4950148f","tid":1149353,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5e9bc9afe0f6871f6331e868b2891b487f6b9ff7","tid":1149353,"uid":33878,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T08:00:35.000Z","msg":"我個隻都會<br />\n病從口入呀<br />\n屌極都唔聽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T08:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd745a37ffb62457b46aeb9c1ada2c1ab202ca65","tid":1149353,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:56:15.000Z","msg":"兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n無視主人的誤會而被棄養：其實兔子側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。兔子也有遠視。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。所以佢地唔係無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n以下2個videos可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=cae88ae8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=95647f6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a><br />\n<br />\n兔子的行為解釋網站：<br />\n<br />\n香港兔協: <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2Fknowledge8_ch.php&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=403f924b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php</a><br />\n<br />\n美國兔協 House Rabbit Society (教育網站): <a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=4d91163f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n<br />\n詳盡身體語言解釋(喜怒哀樂): <a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=95c2a886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"b2005f82aea63b53da84f781f5617d04867fe1d3","tid":1149353,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T13:56:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>兔子開心到極! 🌟🐰</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。兔子也會舒適地躺在地上，伸展手腳，還會打翻騰。室內飼養會比室外養長命，因為沒有天氣和敵人威脅，感到安全、平靜和舒適。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會嚇驚兔子。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom(撫摸/親吻)牠們，令牠們冷靜下來知道是沒事的。我家的兔子一聽到吸塵機聲音就嚇驚，所以每次我工人吸塵的時候，我會一直撫摸他們，幾次後他們已習慣了 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=fdfe48d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE90ikFGQTqs&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=00706650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs</a>"},{"pid":"0dae96da78f86993bb6851b7273271689e72b2cc","tid":1149353,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>怎樣簡單地同兔子剪指甲？</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n這個方法剪指甲是最容易(美國兔子協會的video)，把兔子放在桌上剪，桌上放條毛巾給他站著因為有traction。這方法對兔子來說比較少壓力(stress), 越少壓力越容易，越多人反而越大壓力：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/W9KemnaTGIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FW9KemnaTGIs&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=b2dd8db0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/W9KemnaTGIs</a> <br />\n<br />\n記住不要反轉隻兔仔放在你大髀上好似bb咁，因為會令到牠進入昏睡狀態，心臟跳動越來越慢，有些兔仔因為咁而死去<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O3s6UiCIS3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO3s6UiCIS3I&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=5fe118e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O3s6UiCIS3I</a><br />\n<br />\n我見過有寵物店反轉佢好似BB咁來剪指甲，所以原來好多人都唔知。"},{"pid":"88c35e8621f3bed8f7b4270ace46662c204a89a1","tid":1149353,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"兔子發夢同主人玩：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs-7b9X5x_Ro&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=91070991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro</a>"},{"pid":"e988f9ede1413850b8856a352cb9f33420f3a6a7","tid":1149353,"uid":202354,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:46:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gVOl9HoWgc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9gVOl9HoWgc&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=90075e00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gVOl9HoWgc</a>"},{"pid":"38bea89b716249d725f37a25e20eda997356410f","tid":1149353,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T14:00:17.000Z","msg":"兔子發夢飲水<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkoTWmdwLlp8&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=809e97ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8</a>"},{"pid":"d3059eeabb98dd0efeea011d6b0973cca7e6fd2e","tid":1149353,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:15:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=glFoLbD9muE&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DglFoLbD9muE%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=83ebe8f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=glFoLbD9muE&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"0287c75e183a07833a1efa59eeb8adf432776c58","tid":1149353,"uid":35382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"我入黎係睇女的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce49798fbed983201f0d732c5c565316dda8ad6","tid":1149353,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T08:12:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>兔子會不會叫? 是會的....</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n開心時會「<span style=\"color: red;\">屋屋</span>」聲叫：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mPoSiZmzo58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmPoSiZmzo58&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=4fd0c71d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mPoSiZmzo58</a><br />\n<br />\n不滿時會<span style=\"color: red;\">咕咕叫</span>。後腳大力踏地代表不滿，但也可以代表驚慌覺得有危險，要看當時的情況。在大自然內，兔子後腳大力踏地是用來警告其他兔仔(包括你)有危險。當兔子遇到巨大驚慌或痛苦也會<span style=\"color: red;\">尖叫</span>，例如被捕獵者(predatory animals)追殺和吃的時候，當然這情況是很慘。 <br />\n<br />\n以下video 可看到<span style=\"color: red;\">咕咕叫</span>。當牠用鼻碰主人的手然後縮低代表想被撫摸: <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ8wfR7k3844&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=23a66230\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844</a>"},{"pid":"9134103cdc1f8fe2948e5193f147b60a52db801b","tid":1149353,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0287c75e183a07833a1efa59eeb8adf432776c58","tid":1149353,"uid":35382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T02:22:36.000Z","msg":"我入黎係睇女的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29efe5059b40bdeab5ab2bcabb903d8d7e3ed820","tid":1149353,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:43:09.000Z","msg":"兔子不滿吃飯時被拍攝，上前搞灣2部攝錄機<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lE5Qexr-jos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlE5Qexr-jos&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=10b5a68d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lE5Qexr-jos</a>"},{"pid":"d3c99247084b40059b4880af2c30bb31610729a3","tid":1149353,"uid":229834,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e988f9ede1413850b8856a352cb9f33420f3a6a7","tid":1149353,"uid":202354,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:46:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gVOl9HoWgc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9gVOl9HoWgc&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=90075e00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gVOl9HoWgc</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"ching幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你同啲入扒房扮牛叫<br />\n<br />\n煩住人唔准人食牛嘅傻西動物撚有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGet a life<br />\n<br />\n得閒出去行下街識下人<br />\n<br />\n上下興趣班，學門手藝好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:非兔撚非動物撚<br />\n<br />\n純粹覺得你好無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0712684fa77f0ffb297bbb97b92fd19012b047","tid":1149353,"uid":59221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3c99247084b40059b4880af2c30bb31610729a3","tid":1149353,"uid":229834,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e988f9ede1413850b8856a352cb9f33420f3a6a7","tid":1149353,"uid":202354,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T07:46:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gVOl9HoWgc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9gVOl9HoWgc&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=90075e00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9gVOl9HoWgc</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T11:51:33.000Z","msg":"ching幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你同啲入扒房扮牛叫<br />\n<br />\n煩住人唔准人食牛嘅傻西動物撚有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGet a life<br />\n<br />\n得閒出去行下街識下人<br />\n<br />\n上下興趣班，學門手藝好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:非兔撚非動物撚<br />\n<br />\n純粹覺得你好無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T12:09:59.000Z","msg":"child登不嬲好多人覺得唱反調好撚型架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957df56bb911a3a859fcb36681e5a7182d5e53bc","tid":1149353,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T14:10:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>領養了兔子,係咁跳兔子舞!</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMu27kYckovg&d=0%2BTJGVp%2BJnQ%2Fy6oFhB9FUPkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=0c37aa89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg</a>"}]}